name: INFINITE CHAOS | ISSUE 3/4
description:
an ever flowing river of random glyphs flickering through every conceivable combination of colours and characters

watch in wonder as you witness a handful of an infinite supply of potential; does the ever flowing tide not embody what it truly means to be one unique human among an endless stream of equally unique conscious and subconscious beings?

this is an open edition to celebrate 5k followers. remaining copies will be burnt in 36 hours, and the number of remaining editions will be used as an input variable in a future nft
